{"tid":1247280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係咪loop警察比人射波嘅片比佢地睇?同埋播警察誓詞比佢地聽?","createTime":"2019-06-21T04:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:13:38.000Z","uid":102343,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4c78129f6d470ce4732132a3e3f3a587c68527","tid":1247280,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"要令佢地諗下自己要serve 嘅係邊個。<br />\n<br />\n而家唔好叫黑警同警犬，佢地只會變得更癲，要搶番道德高地同埋要令成件事變得係<span style=\"color: red;\">我地幫緊警察家屬</span>。<br />\n<br />\n播警察誓詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/videos/360178674734219/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2Fvideos%2F360178674734219%2F&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOezsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=daa7db0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/videos/360178674734219/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n香港警察誓詞<br />\n<br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、<span style=\"color: red;\">不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人</span>及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從<span style=\"color: red;\">上級長官的一切合法命令</span>。<br />\n</span><br />\n[size=5]紅字係佢地違反左嘅野，強調佢地忘記誓詞，唔配做警察。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要強調番只準真正警察服務香港，拒絕一切委任證都冇連誓詞都未講過嘅公安，老解搞亂香港。</span><br />\n<br />\nps:<br />\n有冇人補林鄭射波比前線嘅link?<br />\n同埋補警察家屬鬧爆林鄭嘅link?<br />\n<br />\n最好今晚用埋batman 燈投影上天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd053c9fc40dd19134c0bead9ba9d5858b0fd85e","tid":1247280,"uid":102343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:57:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae2bbfb0f7146223fef47c7d9d9e8f0600a565fa","tid":1247280,"uid":102343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e2e7974d62b4160f51f4